    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Connected之后要authenticate()，成功进入Authenticated。但这里有个超时机制——如果认证太久会auth_timeout()直接跳到Error。",
