    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Authenticated之后要初始化，init_complete()成功就到Ready状态，失败init_error()也是进Error。Ready是正常工作状态，可以disconnect()回Idle。",
